dataset.description: This dataset includes facility details, performance rate, measure score, and the state and national average scores for each of the ICH CAHPS survey metrics that are included in the composite measure, as well as the measure score and the state and national average scores for the overall ICH CAHPS measure included in the PY 2019 ESRD QIP.
